text: Nizhneye Mambetshino () is a rural locality (a village) in Yanybayevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 75 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 112 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Nizhneye Mambetshino
